data.title: Wiz Khalifa & Curren$y stay busy with another video "The Life"
data.meta_description: Check out Wiz Khalifa & Curren$y's "The Life"
data.text: After waiting years for their 2009 collab project, the two are now putting out video after video. Wiz & Spitta just dropped their “Forever Ball” video and now follow it up with another visual for “The Life”. Taking place backstage we see both Wiz & Curren$y chilling with a bunch of people smoking and sipping on champagne. Check out the video below:
